---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../../components/Hero.astro";
---

<Layout title="Data Protection — Rusty Notebooks">
    <div class="chapter-bg" style="--bg-image: url('/images/index.png');">
        <div class="chapter-content container">
            <Hero eyebrow="Return" title="Data Protection" backHref={"/"} />

            <section class="section section-narrative">
                <div class="narrative">
                    <p>
                        This website is operated as a personal music project.
                        Protecting your personal data is important.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Personal data is processed only to the extent necessary
                        to provide a functional and secure website.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Responsible Party</strong><br />
                        Björn Hinnah<br />
                        Address: upon request<br />
                        btwentyfive@web.de
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Hosting</strong><br />
                        This website is hosted via Cloudflare Pages. When visiting
                        the site, technical data (such as IP address, browser type,
                        and access time) may be processed automatically to ensure
                        stability and security. Processing is based on legitimate
                        interest (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR).
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Embedded Content (YouTube)</strong><br />
                        This website includes embedded videos from YouTube (Google
                        Ireland Limited). When interacting with these videos, personal
                        data may be transmitted to YouTube, such as your IP address
                        and usage data.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>External Links</strong><br />
                        This website contains links to external platforms including
                        Spotify, Apple Music, YouTube, Instagram, TikTok, and DistroKid
                        / HyperFollow. When clicking these links, you will be redirected
                        to the respective external provider, where their own privacy
                        policies apply.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Web Analytics</strong><br />
                        This website uses Cloudflare Web Analytics to measure traffic
                        and basic performance metrics. According to Cloudflare, this
                        service works without cookies and does not use client-side
                        storage such as localStorage or sessionStorage. The processing
                        is based on legitimate interest (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR).
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        The collected information is used only to understand
                        website traffic and improve performance.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Your Rights</strong><br />
                        You have the right to request information about your stored
                        data, its origin, recipients, and the purpose of processing.
                        You also have the right to request correction or deletion
                        of your data.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        If you have any questions regarding data protection, you
                        can contact the responsible party at any time.
                    </p>

                    <p class="narrative-final">
                        This site is built to share music — nothing more,
                        nothing hidden.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- chapter-content -->
        </div>
        <!-- chapter-bg -->
    </div></Layout
>
